title: Anastasia Konkina
summary: Anastasia Aleksandrovna Konkina (Russian: Анастасия Александровна Конкина; born 1 December 1993) is a Russian judoka.She participated at the 2018 World Judo Championships, winning a medal.
content:
Anastasia Aleksandrovna Konkina (Russian: Анастасия Александровна Конкина; born 1 December 1993) is a Russian judoka.She participated at the 2018 World Judo Championships, winning a medal.
